# Project Overview
This project is a Drive-like document management system with role-based access control and AI capabilities.

# Tech Stack
- Next.js App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Clerk for authentication
- Supabase Postgres
- Supabase Storage / S3-compatible
- Pinecone (or Supabase vector) for AI embeddings
- OpenAI for AI responses

# Core Principles
- Permissions must be enforced server-side.
- AI must never see redacted or unauthorized content.
- Redaction removes content permanently.